                <note rend="inline" type="source">851T.00/59a: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Consul at Dakar (<persName type="to">Flexer</persName>)</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1942-11-25">November 25,
                            1942</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>119. Please report in clear in so far as you can what the situation is and
                    developments as they occur.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
